  "texts": [
    "Such considerations can advance our knowledge regarding success metrics that are not merely focused on the technical functioning of the AI system, a topic discussed in the next section.",
    "This section considers the challenge of translating highly theoretical RAI principles that are difficult to quantify or even observe into measurable outcomes is a considerable challenge (Thomas and Uminsky 2020; Stray 2020; Jacobs 2021).",
    "The derived metrics have to be concrete and observable, e.g.",
    "the number of clicks or likes.",
    "Basing such metrics on the RAI principles is essential since the dominant, techno-centric metrics neither resemble the actual user experience, nor the effects and implications of a system's sociotechnical context (Stray 2020; Thomas and Uminsky 2020; Jacobs 2021)."
